<h3 id="labels">Labels</h3>

<ul>
	<li>All form fields must be given labels.</li>
	<li>You must not hide labels unless the surrounding context makes them unnecessary.</li>
	<li>Labels must be aligned above input fields.</li>
	<li>Labels must be positioned to the right of checkboxes and radio buttons.</li>
	<li>Label text must be short, direct and in sentence case.</li>
	<li>You must not use colons at the end of labels.</li>
	<li>Labels must be associated with form fields using the <code>for</code> attribute.</li>
</ul>

