<h3 id="radio-buttons">Radio buttons</h3>

<p>These let users choose a single option from a list.</p>

<ul>
	<li>You must use a select-box if you have more than 10 radio buttons.</li>
	<li>Radio buttons with large hit areas are easier to select with a mouse or touch devices.</li>
	<li>You must only pre-select options for the user if there’s a strong, user-centred reason to do this.</li>
	<li>The label must be clickable.</li>
</ul>

